                    "prefix": "\n                        \n                    \n                \n                \n                    \n                        When we first formulated the LGLC project in December 2010, we envisaged a straightforward online publication of Lesbian and Gay Liberation in Canada: A Selected Annotated Chronology, 1964–1975, a groundbreaking work by Donald McLeod, a long-time volunteer at the Canadian Lesbian and Gay Archives and a librarian at",
